@startuml vllm_eplb_component
title vLLM EPLB - 组件/数据流概览

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam wrapWidth 240
skinparam maxMessageSize 120

package "vLLM" {
  [GPUModeRunner\n(vllm/v1/worker/gpu_model_runner.py)] as GMR
  [EplbState\n(vllm/distributed/eplb/eplb_state.py)] as ES
  [DefaultEplbPolicy\n(vllm/distributed/eplb/policy/default.py)] as POL
  [rebalance_execute\n(vllm/distributed/eplb/rebalance_execute.py)] as EXEC
  [async_worker\n(vllm/distributed/eplb/async_worker.py)] as AW
  [FusedMoE Layer\n(vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/layer.py)] as LAYER
  [eplb_map_to_physical_and_record\n(vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/fused_moe.py)] as MAPREC
  [MixtureOfExperts Model\n(expert_weights, moe_layers)] as MOE
  [EP ProcessGroup\n(get_ep_group().device_group)] as EPG
}

note right of ES
  核心状态:
  - physical_to_logical_map  (layers, num_physical_experts)
  - logical_to_physical_map  (layers, num_logical_experts, max_slots)
  - logical_replica_count    (layers, num_logical_experts)
  - expert_load_pass         (layers, num_physical_experts)
  - expert_load_window       (window, layers, num_physical_experts)
  - step_interval/window_size/use_async/policy
end note

note right of MAPREC
  路由阶段做两件事:
  1) logical expert -> physical expert\n   (按 replica_count 做确定性“伪随机”挑选)
  2) expert_load_view.scatter_add_ 累加 token 计数
end note

GMR --> ES : 初始化/持有 EPLB 状态\n(enable_eplb)
GMR --> MOE : load_model()
ES --> MOE : add_model()\nmodel.set_eplb_state(...)
LAYER --> MAPREC : forward 时调用\n(enable_eplb)
MAPREC --> ES : 写入 expert_load_pass\n(实际上写入的是 layer 的 expert_load_view)

ES --> POL : policy.rebalance_experts()\n(输入: global logical load window)
POL --> ES : 输出新映射:\nphy2log / log2phy / logcnt

ES --> EXEC : rearrange_expert_weights_inplace()\n(同步模式: 逐层 move_to_buffer/move_from_buffer)
EXEC --> EPG : batch_isend_irecv / all_gather (profile)\n跨 rank 交换 expert rows

ES --> AW : start_async_worker()\n(异步模式: 后台 transfer_layer)
AW --> EXEC : transfer_layer(old,new,layer)\n填充 expert_buffer + CUDA event
GMR --> ES : step()\n每个 forward 后推进
ES --> ES : 更新滑窗 + 计数\n到点触发 rearrange()
ES --> GMR : (异步) move_to_workspace()\n主线程落盘并更新 mapping

legend left
  === 关键点 ===
  - 统计: 在 MoE 路由阶段直接统计 physical expert 的 token 计数
  - 汇总: physical->logical (scatter_add) + all_reduce 得到全局逻辑负载
  - 决策: DeepSeek 风格 packing+replication(+hierarchical) 计算新布局
  - 生效: P2P 交换权重行 + 更新 mapping，使后续路由命中新的 physical slots
endlegend

@enduml


@startuml vllm_eplb_sequence
title vLLM EPLB - 一次周期 (统计→触发→重排→生效) 时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 140
skinparam wrapWidth 240

participant "GPUModeRunner\n(gpu_model_runner.py)" as GMR
participant "MixtureOfExperts Model\n(expert_weights)" as MOE
participant "FusedMoE Layer\n(layer.py)" as LAYER
participant "eplb_map_to_physical_and_record\n(fused_moe.py)" as MAPREC
participant "EplbState\n(eplb_state.py)" as ES
participant "DefaultEplbPolicy\n(policy/default.py)" as POL
participant "rebalance_execute\n(rebalance_execute.py)" as EXEC
participant "EP Group\n(get_ep_group())" as EPG
participant "async_worker\n(async_worker.py)" as AW

== 初始化 ==
GMR -> ES : ES = EplbState(parallel_config, device)
GMR -> MOE : load_model()
GMR -> ES : add_model(MOE, model_config, ...)\n构建初始 mapping + buffers
ES -> MOE : model.set_eplb_state(expert_load_pass,\n logical_to_physical_map,\n logical_replica_count)

== 每个 forward: 路由统计 ==
LAYER -> MAPREC : topk_ids(logical) + maps + load_view
MAPREC -> MAPREC : logical->physical\n(replica_indices = pos % replica_count)
MAPREC -> MAPREC : expert_load_view.scatter_add_(physical_id, +1)
MAPREC --> LAYER : 返回 topk_ids(physical)\n用于 dispatch/combine

== forward 结束: 推进 EPLB ==
GMR -> ES : eplb_step()\nES.step(is_dummy/is_profile, log_stats)
ES -> ES : 若非 dummy:\nload_pass 写入 load_window[step]\nload_pass 清零\nstep++ (ring buffer)
ES -> ES : expert_rearrangement_step++\n到达 step_interval?

alt 未到触发点
  ES --> GMR : return
else 到达触发点: rearrange()
  ES -> ES : 汇总窗口统计\nphysical_load_window -> logical_load_window\n(scatter_add on mapping)
  ES -> EPG : all_reduce(logical_load_window)\n得到全局 logical load

  ES -> POL : rebalance_experts(weight=global_logical_load,\n num_replicas, num_groups, num_nodes, num_ranks,\n old_global_expert_indices)
  POL --> ES : new_phy2log/new_log2phy/new_logcnt

  alt 同步模式(或 profile)
    ES -> EXEC : rearrange_expert_weights_inplace(old_phy2log,\n new_phy2log, expert_weights, ep_group)
    loop each MoE layer
      EXEC -> EPG : batch_isend_irecv (send/recv expert rows)
      EXEC -> EXEC : move_to_buffer + move_from_buffer\n本地 copy / 远端 recv / duplicate
    end
    ES -> ES : 更新 mapping 张量\nphysical_to_logical_map/logical_to_physical_map/logical_replica_count
  else 异步模式(use_async)
    ES -> ES : 保存 new maps 到 model_state.new_*\n标记 rebalanced=True
    ES -> AW : rearrange_event.set()\n唤醒后台线程
    AW -> EXEC : transfer_layer(layer=k)\n异步发起 P2P 收发到 expert_buffer
    note right of AW
      后台线程逐层:
      - buffer_lock 保护
      - CUDA stream + event 记录完成
      - ep_buffer_ready=1 让主线程消费
    end note
    loop 主线程在后续 step() 里轮询
      ES -> EPG : all_reduce(buffer_ready flag)\n所有 rank buffer_ready?
      ES -> ES : move_to_workspace():\n等待 CUDA event\nmove_from_buffer 到真正权重\n更新该层 mapping\nlayer_to_transfer++
    end
    ES -> ES : 所有层完成后 post_eplb()\n清理 new_*，rebalanced=False
  end
end

== 生效 ==
note over LAYER,MAPREC
  新 mapping 生效后:\n下一次路由 MAPREC 会把 logical expert\n映射到“新的 physical slots”，并继续累计新窗口统计
end note

@enduml


